      • name

        private java.lang.String name
        Stores the name of the location

      • interfaces

        private java.util.ArrayList<UserInterface> interfaces
        Stores the interfaces of the location.

        The interfaces are in order of appearance.

        Set to an empty ArrayList of UserInterfaces.

      • allChoices

        private java.util.ArrayList<Choice> allChoices
        Stores all choices of this location.

        Set to an empty ArrayList of Choices.

      • possibleChoices

        private java.util.ArrayList<Choice> possibleChoices
        Stores all choices of this location that meet their own requirements.

        Set to an empty ArrayList of Choices.

      • allPremethods

        private java.util.ArrayList<TFMethod> allPremethods
        Stores all premethods of this location.

        premethods are methods that are invoked when the player moves here.

        Set to an empty ArrayList of TFMethods.

      • possiblePremethods

        private java.util.ArrayList<TFMethod> possiblePremethods
        Stores all premethods of this location that meet their own requirements.

        Set to an empty ArrayList of TFMethods.

      • allPostmethods

        private java.util.ArrayList<TFMethod> allPostmethods
        Stores all postmethods of this location.

        premethods are methods that are invoked when the player moves away from here.

        Set to an empty ArrayList of TFMethods.

      • possiblePostmethods

        private java.util.ArrayList<TFMethod> possiblePostmethods
        Stores all postmethods of this location that meet their own requirements.

        Set to an empty ArrayList of TFMethods.

      • filterPremethods

        public void filterPremethods​()
        Loops over all premethods and adds all premethods that meet their own requirements to allPremethods.

        Adds valid premethods to a new ArrayList that the possiblePremethods is set to after.
